<title>USA: Vornado closes on $183 mln note.</title>
<headline>Vornado closes on $183 mln note.</headline>
<dateline>SADDLE BROOK, N.J. 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Vornado Realty Trust on Thursday said it completed its acquisition of a mortgage note for $185 million.</p>
<p>The note, with a face value of $193 million, is in default, but is secured by a Manhattan office building at 90 Park Ave.</p>
<p>Vornado is a fully-integrated real estate investment trust.</p>
